title: Oct. 22: Little League roundup
text: Posted Oct. 23, 2015 at 2:00 AM Posted Oct. 23, 2015 at 2:00 AM » Social News Intermediate division Montgomery 10, Port Jervis 0 Montgomery: Michael Flannery 6 scoreless innings, 14 strikeouts; Jayden Bell 2-run home run; Peter Brunetti hit, 2 RBI; Shane Meade hit, RBI. Port Jervis: Luke Gadson 2 hits. Minors division Washingtonville Gold 11, Goshen Blue 0 Washingtonville Gold: Oscar Ciriaco 9 strikeouts in four innings; Nathan Scaglione hit 3-for-3; Andrew Dempsey 2 hits; Joshua Guilamo 2 hits. Goshen Blue: Jon Tetzlaff hit; Matt Boat hit. Wallkill Area 9, Port Jervis Red 8 Wallkill Area: Rocco Futia winning pitcher, 2 hits, 2 runs; Leo Schabilon pitched 2⅔ innings, 2 doubles, 3 RBI. Port Jervis Red: Dawson Keuntje, 2 runs and 2 hits in 3⅔ innings; Chase Mitchell home run. recordonline.com
